##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##
##-------------------------Stress-strain relation of filled nanotube-------------------------##
##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##


##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##
##---------------------------------Static variables------------------------------------------##
##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##


# Variables for MD

variable           dt            equal 0.001     # 1 fs
variable           steps_T_equil equal 20000     # 20 ps
variable           steps_P_equil equal 30000     # 30 ps
variable           tdamp         equal ${dt}*100 # thermostat damping constant
variable           Pdamp         equal ${dt}*1000 # Pdamping constant

##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##
##------------------------------------INITIALIZATION-----------------------------------------##
##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##

processors         1 1 *
units              metal
dimension          3 
boundary           p p p
atom_style         full
newton             on 

##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##
##--------------------------------SYSTEM TOPOLOGY INFORMATION--------------------------------##
##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##

read_data          Na4Sn2Ge5O16.lmp  #bulk

##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##
##--------------------------------------FORCE FIELDS-----------------------------------------##
##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##

pair_style         mace no_domain_decomposition
pair_coeff         * * 2024-01-07-mace-128-L2_epoch-199.model-lammps.pt Li Co Ni O


##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##
##-------------------------------run for getting the geometry--------------------------------##
##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##


##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##
##------------------------------------Initial velocities-------------------------------------##
##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##

velocity           all create $T ${rseed} rot yes mom yes


thermo              100
dump                100 all xyz 1 dump1.xyz
run                 10000